INSERT INTO "tmdb_cache" ("cache_key","data","expires_at") VALUES('search:scu','{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/1hS9huDDGeirdy1Regli71wo9ot.jpg","genre_ids":[16,35,10765],"id":284432,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"勇者のクズ","overview":"In the mid-21st century, Tokyo''s mafia can turn into ether-enhanced Demon Lords, and Braves hunt them down. Yashiro, the Grim Reaper, reluctantly takes a new apprentice named Aki Jogamine, a high school girl training to become a Brave. He soon finds himself dragged into one troublesome case after another. The supernatural story of a scumbag master and his self-proclaimed apprentice begins!","popularity":7.2206,"poster_path":"/kSJv65fW98dUqRD5f0ahLLYoZQN.jpg","first_air_date":"2026-01-11","name":"Scum of the Brave","vote_average":7.25,"vote_count":4},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/lIzz0om5v86hqqQm54pT2Rci67E.jpg","genre_ids":[16,18],"id":69292,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"クズの本懐","overview":"Seventeen-year-old Mugi Awaya and Hanabi Yasuraoka appear to be the ideal couple. They are both pretty popular, and they seem to suit each other well. However, outsiders don''t know of the secret they share. Both Mugi and Hanabi have hopeless crushes on someone else, and they are only dating each other to soothe their loneliness. Mugi is in love with Akane Minagawa, a young teacher who used to be his home tutor. Hanabi is also in love with a teacher, a young man who has been a family friend since she was little. In each other, they find a place where they can grieve for the ones they cannot have, and they share physical intimacy driven by loneliness. Will things stay like this for them forever?","popularity":10.3723,"poster_path":"/nKqw1zze4D1HfTaHDs6rxWii5bf.jpg","first_air_date":"2017-01-13","name":"Scum''s Wish","vote_average":6.425,"vote_count":113},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/pag6wzYBW6Jl7stodN5NuZJc8j7.jpg","genre_ids":[18,35],"id":272022,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"あのクズを殴ってやりたいんだ","overview":"Hokomi Sato has hit rock bottom after being left at the altar on her wedding day. However, things start looking up when she meets the kind and compassionate Kairi Kuzuya. But in fact, he turns out to be the “worst womanizing scum of the earth!” Vowing never to be hurt again, Hokomi decides to change herself and takes up boxing, setting her life on a new course. Yet, she can’t seem to keep Kairi out of her life as she begins to learn of his eventful past. Follow Hokomi on her journey to mental and physical empowerment through this no-holds-barred boxing love story!","popularity":3.8611,"poster_path":"/sV9aVWy1UygFynfRzrKSVQzdQ9k.jpg","first_air_date":"2024-10-08","name":"I Wanna Punch That Scumbag!","vote_average":7,"vote_count":5},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/fo2n69P5c8c4FScikpeFu4B1ydr.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":69812,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"クズの本懐","overview":"Seventeen-year-old Mugi Awaya and Hanabi Yasuraoka appear to be the ideal couple. They are both pretty popular, and they seem to suit each other well. However, outsiders don''t know of the secret they share. Both Mugi and Hanabi have hopeless crushes on someone else, and they are only dating each other to soothe their loneliness. Mugi is in love with Akane Minagawa, a young teacher who used to be his home tutor. Hanabi is also in love with a teacher, a young man who has been a family friend since she was little. In each other, they find a place where they can grieve for the ones they cannot have, and they share physical intimacy driven by loneliness. Will things stay like this for them forever?","popularity":3.2641,"poster_path":"/sqDJjwIvFikC4NnChALWuJazUxk.jpg","first_air_date":"2017-01-18","name":"Scum''s Wish","vote_average":5.3,"vote_count":19},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/gT7AbSpkRmjvWuOjMlUQiJHImdF.jpg","genre_ids":[16,18,10765,35],"id":109329,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"穿书自救指南","overview":"Shen Yuan must find a way to befriend Luo Binghe so that he has no reason to seek revenge on his teacher in the future. But with the set series of tragedies meant to befall the protagonist at the hands of Shen Qingqiu, this teacher has his work cut out for him.","popularity":2.5282,"poster_path":"/hG0wkPDPF5IMH4DhiRWN4w7u6Eq.jpg","first_air_date":"2020-09-10","name":"Scumbag System","vote_average":6.9,"vote_count":9},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/h6PwnP6csyI7lsNRo14MhjG1ATm.jpg","genre_ids":[18,35],"id":34748,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"弁護士のくず","overview":"Bengoshi no Kuzu is a Japanese manga written and illustrated by Hideo Iura about Takeda Masami, a new lawyer and fellow lawyer Kuzu Motohito, who Takeda is teamed up with, and how they deal with different court cases. It was serialized in Big Comic Original. Bengoshi no Kuzu received the Shogakukan Manga Award for seinen/general category in 2007.\n\nThe manga was adapted into a 12-episode TV drama, which was broadcast on Tokyo Broadcasting System between April 13, 2006 and June 29, 2006.","popularity":2.0558,"poster_path":"/yKLzn0fY72BRSnaYNmbmbVlj9oJ.jpg","first_air_date":"2006-04-13","name":"Scum of Lawyers","vote_average":5.7,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/d8WmmcZYNKPxxB5wUyv0fhrUT0z.jpg","genre_ids":[10759,10765,80,18],"id":86776,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"シークレット・ミッション Type TOKUJO","overview":"How was Tomari Shinnosuke recruited to the Special Crimes Unit? The mystery lies within the murder casefiles.","popularity":1.315,"poster_path":"/jmGJDmiPsAghuSsZEybE1HHfO07.jpg","first_air_date":"2015-04-08","name":"Kamen Rider Drive: Secret Missions - Type SCU","vote_average":8,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/tVOvd196mtudXppgaIrlDcCVivQ.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":227211,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"犬と屑","overview":"Sakuraba Haruma''s childhood friend Inukai Shuji was a cut above him in every way imaginable, living out the glamorous life bestowed upon him. Haruma, an unassuming salaryman, has lived his every day clutching onto his inferiority complex, existing only in Shuji''s shadow. One day, Haruma coincidentally meets Shuji''s wife, Inukai Reika, who Haruma has always secretly admired since his high school days. With feelings of envy, jealousy, and more, a \"secret\" is born from Haruma''s repetitive days.","popularity":2.3056,"poster_path":"/rTuQwtDp51XrGl1xvSEfdERpUu3.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-06-08","name":"Dog and Scum","vote_average":10,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/uX16JseYVNnJXXQDvx8eA5xojXp.jpg","genre_ids":[99],"id":274966,"origin_country":["IT"],"original_language":"it","original_name":"Scugnizzi per sempre","overview":"The human and sporting experience of a group of \"scugnizzi\" from Caserta who, in Italy in the 80s and 90s, dared to challenge the Olympus of Italian basketball.","popularity":0.112,"poster_path":"/1Cch5F8FuT8vKbwyu4NCq2O16N.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-08-21","name":"Scugnizzi forever","vote_average":7.5,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/toBQga5GIYS2ZP6FnLJlIvJUjSA.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":309245,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"塑光","overview":"The story follows a self-absorbed asset, accustomed to seeing certain people as \"easy prey.\" But everything changes when he crosses paths with a seemingly innocent, gentle, and delicate boy. However, this is just an appearance. The \"prey\" is actually a wolf in sheep''s clothing, who can turn the tables when least expected. Between manipulation, attraction, and hidden secrets, the two begin an emotional game where nothing is exactly what it seems.","popularity":0.4044,"poster_path":"/dy3EYOBKsVR62g7ymmP2xdVFxnI.jpg","first_air_date":"2025-12-26","name":"Sculpted Light","vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_