Blackmailing antagonist Lou Siyi with info from the comments, the \"cannon fodder\" and villain develop feelings despite the manga’s rules. Forced to fight the narrative, they unite to save their fates and forbidden love.","popularity":1.553,"poster_path":"/mZVQ3dGNMnZQdxswJbKlKxMLRBK.jpg","first_air_date":"2026-03-12","name":"Fate Beyond Script","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ar6FhHkxg8E2G0n86Vcmp1lYmyC.jpg","genre_ids":[10764],"id":94233,"origin_country":["GB"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrapyard Supercar","overview":"Each episode, Pro driver Shane Lynch sets two teams of mechanics a task of epic proportions... to build a one-off vehicle from scrapyard junk that can out-perform his top-of-the range supercar. During four manic days, the teams are expertly guided by head-engineer Ralph Hosier, before they hit the racetrack aiming to topple Shane’s four wheeled icon. From acceleration to braking, handling to grip, the series gets under the hood of supercar engineering.","popularity":0.3691,"poster_path":"/uGflcYEEszUftcv4uZcoX0DXqHW.jpg","first_air_date":"2019-08-04","name":"Scrapyard Supercar","vote_average":7,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/5wQVbEsjxle2MZv8I4Jo2lPIhGq.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10759,10765,18,10751,9648],"id":19374,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"ワンダービートS","overview":"The 13-year-old Benny''s father has mysteriously disappeared on an expedition to Sirius. Almost at the same time, attacks start from the alien intars to the Earth dwellers. They implant themselves in the bodies of the inhabitants of the earth.  Due to the mysterious disappearance of Benny''s father, he is accused of making common cause with the intars. Benny, who has remained behind, suffers greatly from these accusations and hopes one day to be able to unravel the mystery of his father''s disappearance and that of the intars. He joins the \"White Pegasus,\" a special unit to combat the Intars and fight together with them against the aliens in the human body. For this, they scale a spaceship down to microscopic size and infiltrate it into the infested body.","popularity":3.8771,"poster_path":"/sANObp3VXgxPqNtGUIS81tSUUGb.jpg","first_air_date":"1986-01-02","name":"Wonder Beat Scramble","vote_average":10,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jvvOFS0sBlDxZax9iwPtrX8aKi6.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":282773,"origin_country":["PT"],"original_language":"pt","original_name":"O Grito","overview":"Vitória Neves, a strong woman and dedicated teacher, always focused on solving the problems of her students and colleagues, even if this means leaving her personal life and family balance behind. The ones who suffer most are Pedro, her teenage son, and Salvador, her husband. Sofia Neves, Vitória''s sister, an artist who lives in London, is opening her first major exhibition when she receives the news of Vitória''s suicide.","popularity":1.852,"poster_path":"/7KGc2rsNoGXmI3sSLNUUtSE2gWa.jpg","first_air_date":"2025-09-16","name":"The Scream","vote_average":1,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/pAl3C198EqNoBfiGKv0Vf9IlBrw.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":135969,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"スナックキズツキ","overview":"Toko runs a small restaurant named Snack Kizutsuki, (Snack Bar of wounds). Her restaurant serves snacks, but doesn''t sell alcohol. She welcomes her customers, who carry wounds in their minds.","popularity":3.2501,"poster_path":"/kMoV6WvrfXrMjYrJoIjlgVCCgJ2.jpg","first_air_date":"2021-10-09","name":"Snack Scratches","vote_average":6,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/3wssj86c6b2WQLWGF8BTF2oRG02.jpg","genre_ids":[9648,35],"id":62046,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scream Queens","overview":"The super-charged comedy-horror series is a modern take on the classic whodunit with a killer cast. ","popularity":13.2626,"poster_path":"/yeayXZYSU8xdmC8i5g5jTdxeggp.jpg","first_air_date":"2015-09-22","name":"Scream Queens","vote_average":7.852,"vote_count":1793},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[],"id":240417,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"2023爱奇艺尖叫之夜","overview":"","popularity":2.5888,"poster_path":"/hqRAuXKusyux52KIW4y2G7SE9cT.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-11-25","name":"2023 iQIYI Scream Night","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}],"total_pages":13,"total_results":244}','2026-04-07 05:11:50');
INSERT INTO "tmdb_cache" ("cache_key","data","expires_at") VALUES('search:Scrub','{"page":1,"results":[{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/vIqDfrp6ApLxM9yRg3xDnQqXy0T.jpg","genre_ids":[35],"id":4556,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrubs","overview":"In the unreal world of Sacred Heart Hospital, John \"J.D.\" Dorian learns the ways of medicine, friendship and life.","popularity":81.4893,"poster_path":"/w7ri7byEYLdciSZOwWHj6TUAX7j.jpg","first_air_date":"2001-10-02","name":"Scrubs","vote_average":7.945,"vote_count":56},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/em2Jzx5QyBTVI7gKipCoE0kG4ot.jpg","genre_ids":[35],"id":295778,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrubs","overview":"J.D. & Turk scrub in together for the first time in a long time–medicine has changed, interns have changed, but their bromance has stood the test of time. Characters new and old navigate the waters of Sacred Heart with laughter, heart and some surprises along the way.","popularity":19.5872,"poster_path":"/nNNM50G7p9C3n4vgidCiybsIdHA.jpg","first_air_date":"2026-02-25","name":"Scrubs","vote_average":8.1,"vote_count":33},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/66REbPMYhTZNnEqM9btmXJcCOqZ.jpg","genre_ids":[18,80],"id":234212,"origin_country":["AU"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrublands","overview":"In a small town, a priest opens fire on his congregation, killing five parishioners. One year later, a journalist arrives to investigate the tragedy, and after digging beneath the surface finds himself in a life-and-death race to uncover the truth.","popularity":3.0891,"poster_path":"/iFRUtxh7OHLqoER6oflO6DWNaQJ.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-11-16","name":"Scrublands","vote_average":7.3,"vote_count":25},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[35],"id":17486,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrubs: Interns","overview":"A web series following four interns in their first year at Sacred Heart Hospital—Katie Collins, Denise \"Jo\" Mahoney, Howie Gelder and Sonja \"Sunny\" Dey, who \"directs\" the series as a video diary project.","popularity":0.9112,"poster_path":"/aLkyDFtUlxIG9lI6PWV0ytFfL8A.jpg","first_air_date":"2009-01-01","name":"Scrubs: Interns","vote_average":5.222,"vote_count":18},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[10764],"id":207868,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Scrubbing In","overview":"\"Scrubbing In\" follows a group of travel nurses working in a CA hospital for 13 weeks. Relocating from across the country, these nurses have left their lives behind for short-term hospital contracts, with the added benefit of exploring a new city.","popularity":0.1858,"poster_path":"/9guKe03ni6iIcx39lxyQb1Orcr6.jpg","first_air_date":"2013-10-24","name":"Scrubbing In","vote_average":7,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[99],"id":38053,"origin_country":["GB"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Wormwood Scrubs","overview":"","popularity":0.0071,"poster_path":null,"first_air_date":"2010-05-10","name":"Wormwood Scrubs","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":6}','2026-04-07 05:11:51');
