king up in a strange virtual world with no recollection of the past, Hakuno finds himself forced to fight for survival in a war he does not understand for a prize beyond value; the opportunity to have one''s wish granted. With only an enigmatic \"Servant\" by his side, Hakuno Kishinami will have to face both friends and foes in battles to the death in order to not only gain possession of a mysterious object known as the \"Holy Grail,\" but also to find the answer to the most important question of all: \"Who am I?\"","popularity":6.712,"poster_path":"/5qveZHKo8RatUbZDzgGG9QEj558.jpg","first_air_date":"2018-01-28","name":"Fate/Extra Last Encore","vote_average":7.3,"vote_count":97},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/mhlT8wIYlsjKK5tRASsALxePkLG.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10765],"id":213326,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"悲劇の元凶となる最強外道ラスボス女王は民の為に尽くします。","overview":"Pride Royal Ivy is only eight years old when she realizes that she''s been reincarnated, destined to become the future wicked queen and final boss of an otome game. She''s got it all in this new life: razor-sharp wit, boss-tier powers, and influence over the kingdom as crown princess. Determined to sow despair and destruction across the land, she... Wait, what kind of a rotten future is that?! Princess Pride decides to drop the maniacal villainess plan and protect the male love interests instead, cheating her way to saving everyone she can! Will this final boss end up earning the adoration of her kingdom?","popularity":15.3143,"poster_path":"/u6bMg0g9KDw9nTuMqORCYWHsMSe.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-07-07","name":"The Most Heretical Last Boss Queen: From Villainess to Savior","vote_average":8.1,"vote_count":55},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/lY2DhbA7Hy44fAKddr06UrXWWaQ.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":100088,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last of Us","overview":"Twenty years after modern civilization has been destroyed, Joel, a hardened survivor, is hired to smuggle Ellie, a 14-year-old girl, out of an oppressive quarantine zone. What starts as a small job soon becomes a brutal, heartbreaking journey, as they both must traverse the United States and depend on each other for survival.","popularity":62.4709,"poster_path":"/dmo6TYuuJgaYinXBPjrgG9mB5od.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-01-15","name":"The Last of Us","vote_average":8.439,"vote_count":6887},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/q31EEBycbOyX7GGJP4GTPI5WJRO.jpg","genre_ids":[10767,35,10763],"id":60694,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Last Week Tonight with John Oliver","overview":"A half-hour satirical look at the week in news, politics and current events.","popularity":43.8037,"poster_path":"/fuuEjEr69uvRtGaQw70JfvdrUwb.jpg","first_air_date":"2014-04-27","name":"Last Week Tonight with John Oliver","vote_average":7.817,"vote_count":785},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/5Ig66JHWuqotsTwtU2P8zg3TJhv.jpg","genre_ids":[99,18],"id":103026,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Undertaker: The Last Ride","overview":"The anticipated WWE Network docuseries will look back on The Undertaker’s storied WWE career and place a focus on the ongoing challenges the wrestling legend appears to have with a career beginning to near it''s end.","popularity":4.044,"poster_path":"/ckKQrIUD9kKAtuTKEkybcajScyA.jpg","first_air_date":"2020-05-10","name":"Undertaker: The Last Ride","vote_average":7.4,"vote_count":316},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/5ZeU6YQGHMd0jqQCxsE9SpshQw2.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10759,9648,10765],"id":74185,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"少女終末旅行","overview":"Civilization is dead, but Chito and Yuuri are still alive. So they hop aboard their beloved Kettenkrad motorbike and aimlessly wander the ruins of the world they once knew. Day after hopeless day, they look for their next meal and fuel for their ride. But as long as the two are together, even an existence as bleak as theirs has 