 while her path crosses with fashion photographer Atlas Demiroğlu, who came to the police station because of a film full of mysterious images. The investigation, which begins with a woman''s body found in an amusement park, soon opens the doors to a multi-layered puzzle that extends to both Sare and Atlas'' pasts. As each new clue draws Sare and Atlas into a dark labyrinth, the boundaries between reality, fantasy, loyalty and betrayal become increasingly blurred.","popularity":5.9142,"poster_path":"/jwVRYnc6IwReY9bURd2svzJezP6.jpg","first_air_date":"2026-01-16","name":"Last Frame","vote_average":7,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/QbtctI8EzlhsyFDMUMyG3fli8B.jpg","genre_ids":[10759,18,10768],"id":63333,"origin_country":["GB"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Kingdom","overview":"A show of heroic deeds and epic battles with a thematic depth that embraces politics, religion, warfare, courage, love, loyalty and our universal search for identity. Combining real historical figures and events with fictional characters, it is the story of how a people combined their strength under one of the most iconic kings of history in order to reclaim their land for themselves and build a place they call home.","popularity":33.5405,"poster_path":"/8eJf0hxgIhE6QSxbtuNCekTddy1.jpg","first_air_date":"2015-10-10","name":"The Last Kingdom","vote_average":8.245,"vote_count":1926},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/xWb85qKubVjA39rVbBCXLOVl8Kg.jpg","genre_ids":[18,10765],"id":216264,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"神隐","overview":"Yin, a hardworking Shuining Beast, and Gu Jin, the son of the true God whose magic has been sealed, meet by chance and embark on a quest to find Feng Yin''s Immortal Essence. Alongside their companions, Hong Yi of the Fox Clan and Yan Shuang of the Eagle Clan, they face numerous challenges to collect the essence. Battling the villain Qing Lin and his followers, they overcome obstacles and, in the end, not only fulfill their mission to restore peace but also find love, friendship, and family.","popularity":11.8038,"poster_path":"/33zNWhfS3r0xWp7EaXtO9LDoB5Y.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-12-11","name":"The Last Immortal","vote_average":7.2,"vote_count":13},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/kU98MbVVgi72wzceyrEbClZmMFe.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10759,10765],"id":246,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Avatar: The Last Airbender","overview":"In a war-torn world of elemental magic, a young boy reawakens to undertake a dangerous mystic quest to fulfill his destiny as the Avatar, and bring peace to the world.","popularity":22.4839,"poster_path":"/9RQhVb3r3mCMqYVhLoCu4EvuipP.jpg","first_air_date":"2005-02-21","name":"Avatar: The Last Airbender","vote_average":8.8,"vote_count":4750},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/1RYuL7AjKeHkN1h3YQcHMlqqI9z.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10759,10765],"id":68888,"origin_country":["FR"],"original_language":"fr","original_name":"Lastman","overview":"Paxtown, a corrupt capital, torn by crime and preyed by the mafia. In this rotten megalopolis, Richard Aldana, street smart, without ties or ambitions, is a boxer in his off time. But this was all before everything got flipped on its head. Overnight, Aldana finds himself with Siri, a girl targeted by \"The Order of the Lion,\" a religious group that thinks the girl is the key to \"the other world\".","popularity":3.205,"poster_path":"/wr7ew7w2zg3g2xWuSexaKzGXzo3.jpg","first_air_date":"2016-11-22","name":"Lastman","vote_average":7.543,"vote_count":47},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/y8uuJW0uF0ej7EHu1KMQ2mJnfeS.jpg","genre_ids":[10751],"id":135354,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"您好！母亲大人","overview":"A story of hope and despair surrounding the lives of a mother and son from a small town in Subei.\n\nThe 18-year-old Ding Xiao Jun who lives with his mother Ding Bi Yun has been admitted to a university in Beijing. However, as soon as he entered university, 