led its first major and disturbing storyline, the rape of Carly Morris; it was one of the first shows to feature such storylines during the early timeslot. H&A has tackled many adult-themed and controversial storylines; something rarely found in its restricted timeslot.","popularity":34.6854,"poster_path":"/vn0eKMiG69bhQtxb7qLRo8SSqu5.jpg","first_air_date":"1988-01-18","name":"Home and Away","vote_average":6.3,"vote_count":74},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/wfQ5y0vS9Cd4hK03Mhiza9Vry2N.jpg","genre_ids":[10764,10767],"id":195648,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"央视春晚相声小品","overview":"","popularity":42.4916,"poster_path":"/i61poXdAvfQ454cLOV4qdrissOF.jpg","first_air_date":"1983-02-12","name":"CCTV Spring Festival Gala: Crosstalk and Sketch","vote_average":9,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/32iRX9xqNH3ErJN6FowxdtgYmiY.jpg","genre_ids":[35,10764],"id":30801,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"1박 2일","overview":"2 Days & 1 Night is a South Korean reality-variety show with the motto \"real wild road variety.\" Its main concept is to recommend various places of interest that viewers can visit in South Korea.","popularity":60.8455,"poster_path":"/qezeCEkIKHQM5iwyVeYBuXmYA2h.jpg","first_air_date":"2007-08-05","name":"2 Days and 1 Night","vote_average":7.1,"vote_count":29},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/eNjzPQsNNPd8zluKTpv7Axhk8p4.jpg","genre_ids":[10767],"id":1900,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"LIVE with Kelly and Mark","overview":"A morning talk show with A-list celebrity guests, top-notch performances and one-of-a-kind segments that are unrivaled on daytime television, plus spontaneous, hilarious and unpredictable talk.","popularity":36.4157,"poster_path":"/hBkyypWN3EcOzkozatiCm5VeaG.jpg","first_air_date":"1988-09-05","name":"LIVE with Kelly and Mark","vote_average":5.4,"vote_count":48}],"total_pages":300,"total_results":5994}','2026-04-07 06:24:56');
