y of sentient toys, their leader, the wise and caring \"Old Bear\" had disappeared some time ago, having been put into the loft and forgotten. After the toys rescue him and bring him back down to the playroom, Old Bear again becomes their most respected toy. Each episode focuses on the adventures of Old Bear and his loveable friends in and about the playroom.","popularity":0.7474,"poster_path":"/r4VBugitcQFSfgnzJSWICFzkY1k.jpg","first_air_date":"1993-10-03","name":"Old Bear Stories","vote_average":8.5,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/urVjejQouXTjsVAFMaXgy25mwte.jpg","genre_ids":[10759,10764],"id":259488,"origin_country":["CN","GB"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"跟着贝尔去冒险","overview":"Eight celebrities from China, Hong Kong and Taiwan embark on a 16 day adventure in the forests of Southwest China''s Guizhou Province with Bear Grylls and Chinese co-presenter Jiang Changjian.","popularity":3.4562,"poster_path":"/eaHXW7bAlOc9ZaCsJAbSppWFs4b.jpg","first_air_date":"2015-10-16","name":"Survivor Games with Bear Grylls","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}],"total_pages":11,"total_results":208}','2026-04-07 06:28:22');
