,"first_air_date":"2011-07-04","name":"Vic and Bob''s Afternoon Delights","vote_average":10,"vote_count":1},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/n8cf5jBpiOt5z9GqTlsMFBktxzN.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10762,35,10751],"id":72376,"origin_country":["BE","FR"],"original_language":"fr","original_name":"Boule & Bill","overview":"Bobby & Bill is a story of the friendship between a boy and his dog, their gang of friends, lively moments, good humour and gentleness.","popularity":0.9924,"poster_path":"/eXdYOaoViTNbvw1qx8ZYHfRxJFH.jpg","first_air_date":"2016-01-23","name":"Bobby & Bill","vote_average":6,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[],"id":11635,"origin_country":["GB"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Bob''s Full House","overview":"Bob''s Full House was a popular quiz programme hosted by Bob Monkhouse which was based on the popular game ''Bingo'' and aired on BBC1 from 1 September 1984 until 20 January 1990.","popularity":0.2125,"poster_path":"/v6cfh2cmhtdZpDzOyydwhHL23w8.jpg","first_air_date":"1984-09-01","name":"Bob''s Full House","vote_average":8.5,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[],"id":216552,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Dinners of Death","overview":"Proving once again that “the drive-in will never die,” iconic horror host and exploitation movie aficionado Joe Bob Briggs is back with an all-new Shudder Original series, hosting weekly Friday night double features streaming live exclusively on Shudder. Every week, The Last Drive-In series offers an eclectic pairing of films, with selections ranging across five decades and running the gamut from horror classics to obscurities and foreign cult favorites. And from time to time, special surprise guests will drop in on Joe Bob and Darcy the Mail Girl.","popularity":0.6035,"poster_path":"/pYsYXDkONiKb4meDefS26Ums0Rg.jpg","first_air_date":"2018-11-22","name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Dinners of Death","vote_average":10,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/3LjeaukdKsQmPEjhH0r7Uj03q1R.jpg","genre_ids":[],"id":276328,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-In with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Beelzebub Bash","overview":"This Halloween, Joe Bob and Darcy are raising hell on Joe Bob''s Beelzebub Bash, hosting a double-feature so devilish that they''ll need two special guests to handle the necessary pitchforks.","popularity":0.4744,"poster_path":"/beZ88ALaclZ21Ek4IVcD4dGPNrH.jpg","first_air_date":"2024-10-25","name":"The Last Drive-In with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Beelzebub Bash","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/wyk6Qgc9EziG1JMtrMox73RoI4j.jpg","genre_ids":[10764],"id":307890,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"밥플레이스","overview":"","popularity":0.913,"poster_path":"/c2cM25KD0MYjp7tJwcvG4JmJLf7.jpg","first_air_date":"2025-12-02","name":"Bob Place","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[],"id":227294,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Halloween Hoedown","overview":"In what has become an annual tradition, iconic horror host and foremost drive-in movie critic Joe Bob Briggs returns with a special The Last Drive-In double feature just in time for Halloween, this year joined by special guests Halloween Kills: director David Gordon Green and producer Jason Blum.","popularity":0.4626,"poster_path":"/qwovl0DBbcj00rCwwZeTIjVnkwm.jpg","first_air_date":"2021-10-08","name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Halloween Hoedown","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[35,9648,10765],"id":216556,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Joe Bob''s Red Christmas","overview":"Joe Bob, Darcy, and the whole Drive-In crew gather around the yule log for some reindeer games and a triple feature of classic holiday horror films and deep-dive trivia.","popularity":0.1945,"poster_path":"/sJGbiZnBpiCLtNs7VIu4DIXLnfK.jpg","first_air_date":"2019-12-13","name":"Joe Bob''s Red Christmas","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/uQEpUkfliygrZN9gYtswpXPfacp.jpg","genre_ids":[35],"id":246236,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-in with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Very Violent Valentine","overview":"Joe Bob Briggs and Darcy the Mailgirl honor the lusty sting of Cupid''s arrow with a kinky double-feature featuring blood, sex, and the dark side of love.","popularity":0.2224,"poster_path":"/hfGOgwNBDyGyUUf7dkqS7e6sGBM.jpg","first_air_date":"2024-02-09","name":"The Last Drive-in with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Very Violent Valentine","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/oDnmFKtuzykmjJ38mqn8m0tdERc.jpg","genre_ids":[],"id":242071,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-in with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Creepy Christmas","overview":"Joe Bob and Darcy deck the bloody halls with a double-helping of yuletide horror while raising money for the less-fortunate... and this year, they get a little help from Ol'' Saint Nick himself.","popularity":0.3997,"poster_path":"/lBvKUs9DKBgYGCXY01GajDjtIUZ.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-12-15","name":"The Last Drive-in with Joe Bob Briggs: Joe Bob''s Creepy Christmas","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/sqoJC9NFotIWZ534PTyUiUi9Dcv.jpg","genre_ids":[],"id":227275,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Joe Bob’s Vicious Vegas Valentine","overview":"It’s a new year, which means a new slate of holiday specials from horror host Joe Bob Briggs and “The Last Drive-in” on Shudder. Up first is the brand new Valentine’s Day Special, “Joe Bob’s Vicious Vegas Valentine.”\n\nWhat pairs better with matrimony than monsters?\n\nJoe Bob Briggs, Darcy the Mail Girl, and “The Last Drive-in” crew aim to deliver the biggest special yet by leaving behind the trailer part and taking the wedding capital of the world by storm. In addition to a horror double feature centered around “nasty love stories,” the legendary horror host will also officiate the wedding of two fans on-air!","popularity":0.4753,"poster_path":"/kSmE4esLPnbygDuPxYQgrb0AHwQ.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-02-10","name":"Joe Bob’s Vicious Vegas Valentine","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/z01HqofdHg1OMkXJaWbtH1ewPER.jpg","genre_ids":[],"id":225865,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Halloween Hideaway","overview":"Dust off your Ouija Board and crack open a Lone Star, because Joe Bob is back in town just in time for Halloween! Joe Bob, Darcy and the whole Drive-In crew hunker down in a cabin on a certain infamous lake to serve up an extra-spooky double-feature of two films set on All Hallow’s Eve.","popularity":0.5255,"poster_path":"/iV6ycnNrxm1HGDKG3Ac3ppnS0KJ.jpg","first_air_date":"2020-10-23","name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Halloween Hideaway","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[],"id":225862,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Heartbreak Trailer Park","overview":"Love (and a tinge of horror) is in the air for The Last Drive-In’s new special! Joe Bob Briggs will be joined by special guests for a double feature of two unique films that explore the heartbreaking side of Valentine’s Day.","popularity":0.2407,"poster_path":"/t9sgZh4m9Img4FBZT5gX022LHBq.jpg","first_air_date":"2022-02-11","name":"The Last Drive-In: Joe Bob''s Heartbreak Trailer Park","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/ky1s6iLl4mItWAmwQwSek1bvCGB.jpg","genre_ids":[],"id":232051,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Joe Bob''s Ghoultide Get-Together","overview":"Check the date on your eggnog and hang your stockings with care, because this Christmas Joe Bob Briggs and Darcy the Mailgirl continue their annual tradition of raising money for charity by hosting back-to-back tales of Yuletide terror.","popularity":0.1544,"poster_path":"/vtVnYC4hiiGoW7740ZCAmG8t27x.jpg","first_air_date":"2022-12-16","name":"Joe Bob''s Ghoultide Get-Together","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}],"total_pages":3,"total_results":43}','2026-04-07 16:01:59');
