 characters in a story by a long-dead writer named Drosselmeyer, they resist their assigned fates and fight to keep the story from becoming a tragedy.","popularity":8.9949,"poster_path":"/lXPCfdHq3GQxLqTBIQ9QtRZSftS.jpg","first_air_date":"2002-08-16","name":"Princess Tutu","vote_average":8,"vote_count":31},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/4II1SxAXSCrFqJfyuiOhRozTZqc.jpg","genre_ids":[18,10765,35,10751],"id":82199,"origin_country":["FR"],"original_language":"fr","original_name":"Léna - Rêve d''étoile","overview":"When Lena Grisky, a Russian Princess and student at the Paris Opera Ballet School accidentally time travels to present day, she must quickly adapt if she hopes to keep her secret and hide from the dangerous Time Collectors.","popularity":8.0156,"poster_path":"/uOTYMzTlXFbWDZCxxc0vX9CvBsl.jpg","first_air_date":"2018-04-14","name":"Find Me in Paris","vote_average":8.072,"vote_count":132},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/p2JFgczzy4JHRVSzgcyHNvrJItp.jpg","genre_ids":[10751,10759,35,10765,18],"id":59369,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"Spellbound","overview":"Cece Parker Jones'' life is turned upside-down when she discovers she''s a real witch. Magical mayhem ensues at the Paris Opera Ballet School when Cece begins to practice her spell work, making things harder to juggle as she balances new magical identity, dance, and simply being a teenager! Things get even more complicated when she accidentally summons her enemies, a group called the Mystics.","popularity":1.6996,"poster_path":"/t7l0XbTTT8NUISOBfPsop4kHbVc.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-08-31","name":"Spellbound","vote_average":8.1,"vote_count":7}],"total_pages":1,"total_results":5}','2026-04-08 05:41:19');
