orking for some very dangerous people, two deeply incapable siblings become the most disorganized duo in organized crime.","popularity":32.4169,"poster_path":"/mgXTCQ86lV3oudr2KXXO5zGEqIb.jpg","first_air_date":"2026-04-09","name":"Big Mistakes","vote_average":8,"vote_count":5},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/jq0ICtFvYyqk6nse8AAkZkaSsXY.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":212118,"origin_country":["HK"],"original_language":"cn","original_name":"摩登小男人","overview":"","popularity":6.0007,"poster_path":"/zBqahqHGO3lH2fFeC5piAX0B5UJ.jpg","first_air_date":"1992-04-01","name":"Big Little Man","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/5YTC2zOpOYTlHHeGqY2tjYTrnHp.jpg","genre_ids":[10764],"id":236680,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"덩치 서바이벌-먹찌빠","overview":"Although they are bigger than others, Korea''s representative large people who love their bodies have gathered together!\n\nIn this era where fashion, tastes, and tastes are diverse, big people who shout, “My body can become a trend too!” compete for the position of ‘advertising model’, a big survival show that loves my body and cannot gain or lose weight.","popularity":4.3871,"poster_path":"/bOX7TuRUYDhfMb5P9cwcCcSS5JH.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-10-08","name":"Meokjjibba: Big Survival","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/tYRZ9tOerxbi4ZQXdhYB4kacZzM.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":61934,"origin_country":["KR"],"original_language":"ko","original_name":"빅맨","overview":"Kim Ji Hyuk (Kang Ji Hwan) lives a hard knocked life, but when the orphan meets the modest restaurateur Hong Dal Sook (Song Ok Suk), he gains a mother figure and works hard to open his own restaurant one day. Then suddenly, the family behind Korea''s most powerful corporation claims that he is their long lost son. When Ji Hyeok discovers the Hyunsung family''s ulterior motives, he swears to bring down the company that destroyed the life he worked so hard to build.","popularity":3.1945,"poster_path":"/vmkEZd4jAo5ThTb3ZyENj6qizwp.jpg","first_air_date":"2014-04-28","name":"Big Man","vote_average":6.2,"vote_count":5},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/bicAdMelrPOY6ZUgcW94tvpYntu.jpg","genre_ids":[18],"id":83878,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"ビッグマネー!〜浮世の沙汰は株しだい〜","overview":"\"Big Money!\" is a human drama with a suspense twist about a young man who learns the tricks of the trade about stock exchange from a well-experienced investor. The backdrop of this story is the elaborate world of banking and the stock market.","popularity":2.2717,"poster_path":"/ebkwQFEaExPeILtHS6LUzXs7CuF.jpg","first_air_date":"2002-04-11","name":"Big Money","vote_average":6,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/996SZsMPTnm0JADuuUKO5fTEQg3.jpg","genre_ids":[16,35],"id":72452,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"お姉ちゃんが来た","overview":"Tomoya’s father remarries to another woman, giving him a stepsister, Ichika. However Ichika is 17-years old and has completely fallen in love with her stepbrother who is only 13!! Families will collide in the most unusual fashion this season, in the new anime short: ONEE-CHAN GA KITA!","popularity":3.7825,"poster_path":"/jEDeJhl39ryjIKqVthmFN1ZJWFZ.jpg","first_air_date":"2014-01-09","name":"My Big Sister Arrived","vote_average":5,"vote_count":19},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/zqrfc55A5YVaH6jQufaJYIXWjvG.jpg","genre_ids":[16,35,10765],"id":79514,"origin_country":["CN"],"original_language":"zh","original_name":"我家大师兄脑子有坑","overview":"The hilarious adventures of the eldest apprentice of a sect who has a problem with his brain.\n\nDongfang Xianyun is reincarnated as the eldest disciple of the Care-free sect. But the only thing that goes through his mind is to make sure he doesn''t end up dying by the hands of the \"main character\". Read as he makes no sense to his sibling disciples while avoiding flags left and right.","popularity":7.4752,"poster_path":"/dZO9a1A2LfoYvXbK78xNtbFzgsl.jpg","first_air_date":"2018-04-04","name":"What''s Wrong with My Big Brother","vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/cf3V6YMhvuxkgZQrUe1rLOZRvjQ.jpg","genre_ids":[16],"id":69294,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"MARGINAL#4 KISSから創造るBig Bang","overview":"On February 13, as snow flurries dance in the air, a new idol unit is born at Pythagoras Production. They are the idols who will deliver their kiss to the ends of the galaxy: \"Marginal #4.\" Its members, Atom Kirihara, Rui Aiba, L Nomura, and R Nomura, put all their effort into their entertainment career for the sake of the fan supporting them! They continue to mature as idols along with the senior unit pulling the entertainment industry forward, Lagrange Point, and the younger unit preparing to make their debut, Unicorn Jr. But when they step off the stage, they''re ordinary high school boys with some chaotic student lives! This is the tale of Margninal #4, a school slice-of-life about idols that shine brighter than the stars.","popularity":1.0155,"poster_path":"/urhY0sALSGBFtKzqac1Nu0SG8Wg.jpg","first_air_date":"2017-01-12","name":"Marginal#4 Kiss Kara Tsukuru Big Bang","vote_average":7,"vote_count":3},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/gvuvboVnUMY8yYPKJCZVBGmIg9c.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10762],"id":52270,"origin_country":["JP"],"original_language":"ja","original_name":"シートン動物記 くまの子ジャッキー","overview":"Monarch: The Big Bear of Tallac is a Japanese anime TV series consisting in 26 episodes. It was directed by Yoshio Kuroda and was first broadcast on Asahi Broadcasting Corporation in 1977.","popularity":2.3982,"poster_path":"/tV86q906ujvJNH3e1Fca1WGfH3I.jpg","first_air_date":"1977-06-07","name":"Monarch: The Big Bear of Tallac","vote_average":6.4,"vote_count":18},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/dPS8Sm5NUCsWqIVHZRQPW5jkCUE.jpg","genre_ids":[80,18],"id":147051,"origin_country":["RU"],"original_language":"ru","original_name":"Моя большая тайна","overview":"The closed campus of an experimental university on Russian Island. Student Sonya Kimaeva returns from abroad to the academy''s dormitory to investigate the mysterious death of her best friend. But during the time that Sonya was absent, the situation has changed dramatically, and now excerpts from the personal diary of the deceased, replete with shocking details, are in the hands of students and teachers. Every day, more and more new secrets of students and teachers of the Academy become known to everyone, thanks to the anonymous blog \"Your big secret\". And this element cannot be stopped.","popularity":1.4874,"poster_path":"/3W7QXQgzdckLHvXgvl79tgZtURY.jpg","first_air_date":"2021-11-23","name":"My Big Secret","vote_average":3.9,"vote_count":7},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/nOzI0NcyK41SugTUqSwndvSCroq.jpg","genre_ids":[18,35],"id":134686,"origin_country":["RU"],"original_language":"ru","original_name":"Большая секунда","overview":"Estranged ex-lovers, Kostya and Kira are unexpectedly thrown together again when they''re asked to collaborate as script-writers on a love-story set in a music school. The script focuses on teachers Rostislav (Dmitry Lysenkov) and Arina (Evgeniya Borzykh), who are caught-up in a difficult situation, made more complicated by Arina passing off a new colleague as her boyfriend to placate her demanding mother. The real and phoney relationships, both on and off-paper (or in reality or in the script), test all the characters, and examine themes of love, trust, sex, infidelity, friendship, responsibility as well as compatibility.","popularity":1.3683,"poster_path":"/58XOsWyfM5qxP6ABI20nS8wU35H.jpg","first_air_date":"2021-08-06","name":"The Big Moment","vote_average":7.8,"vote_count":10},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"genre_ids":[10764,18],"id":31022,"origin_country":["MX"],"original_language":"es","original_name":"Big Brother Mexico","overview":"Big Brother México is a reality television series based on the international Big Brother format produced in the Netherlands by Endemol. Big Brother México was launched by Televisa in 2002. Before its debut, the idea of being watched twenty-four hours a day by a camera was shocking to some in Mexican society. The series was successful, and it was followed by a special edition called Big Brother VIP with Mexican celebrities from show business and even politics. Congressman Jorge Kahwagi, minority whip of the Mexican Green Party in the Chamber of Deputees of Mexico''s Congress, shocked and angered many people in Mexico when he asked to be excused from his post in Congress to be sequestered for months inside the Big Brother House. Critics among colleagues and the general public accused him of dereliction of duty, discrediting his office, and seeking personal gain. During the show, late-night variety-show host, comedian, and producer Adal Ramones, also from Televisa, made a send-up of Big Brother which he called \"El Gran Carnal\" or \"Big Bro\" in Mexican slang.\n\nIn December 2009, it was announced that there would be an \"Allstars\" version of Big Brother Mexico and that if it favors well with ratings, a possible fourth season will likely follow.","popularity":3.1685,"poster_path":null,"first_air_date":"2002-03-03","name":"Big Brother Mexico","vote_average":2,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/q8B1fV2Aylzj3Y7D7DwyBC8BjuX.jpg","genre_ids":[10759,35,80],"id":57033,"origin_country":["IT"],"original_language":"it","original_name":"Big Man","overview":"The renowned Insurance International Co. has created an enquiry network, headed by detective Jack Clementi,  to defend itself against insurance fraud. Jack has saved the company enormous amounts of money throughout his successful investigations and his bosses are more than willing put up with his brusque manners, his disconcerting frankness, and his intolerance for any form of company bureaucracy. Yet he is a big guy with a huge heart.","popularity":3.8064,"poster_path":"/zzl1YOJ1vda6aEBIerqS53zNI4D.jpg","first_air_date":"1988-11-25","name":"Big Man","vote_average":5.5,"vote_count":2},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/u8EUQWxMVYnUENwAhKyoRE5iBCa.jpg","genre_ids":[10764,18],"id":69880,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"My Big Fat Fabulous Life","overview":"Dancing her way through the haters, Whitney Way Thore is embracing her body in a world that judges people by their size. She navigates both career challenges and relationship snafus with her vivacious personality, a sense of humor and an abundance of courage.\n\nThis series follows Whitney who was diagnosed with an endocrine system disorder called polyscystic ovary syndrome (PCOS) which caused her, a slender dancer at the time, to gain more than 200 pounds in one year at college. Feeling trapped in a big body, she struggled with self-doubt and negative stereotypes. Now 380 pounds and eager to continue sharing her passion for dance, Whitney has learned to embrace her body and love herself again.","popularity":5.0456,"poster_path":"/pdlPdvtGaSiJQ35V6CjAskQB12.jpg","first_air_date":"2015-01-13","name":"My Big Fat Fabulous Life","vote_average":7.3,"vote_count":16},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/kP3cSY4tdRS1M1JrnrGed8bCQ7m.jpg","genre_ids":[16,10762],"id":46759,"origin_country":["BR","CA"],"original_language":"en","original_name":"My Big Big Friend","overview":"Three friends and their three big imaginary friends have adventures.","popularity":3.6097,"poster_path":"/36O35c7L3fPKD1FQiQm5EmLzU4y.jpg","first_air_date":"2010-08-09","name":"My Big Big Friend","vote_average":6.4,"vote_count":8},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/weXOjkzdeFi2NHBVFpj1dy1YcE8.jpg","genre_ids":[9648,18,35],"id":237511,"origin_country":["RU"],"original_language":"ru","original_name":"Теория больших денег","overview":"The genius of mathematics Mikhail Nefedov teaches probability theory and mathematical statistics at the university. He remembers everything he has ever heard, seen or read. Mikhail learns that his teenage son has a dangerous genetic disease, the treatment of which will require a multimillion-dollar sum. After selling the apartment, Nefedov makes a perfectly calculated bet on a local football league match, but loses. He couldn''t have made a mistake, which means there is an unaccounted variable in the equation. And this is an underground betting business where the results of games are rigged to extract illegal income. Mikhail calculates the organizers of the shadow business and demands his winnings from them. This is how the university teacher''s war with the betting mafia begins.","popularity":0.9303,"poster_path":"/5mDJzjKJIDE3NHT7zzzK2rlEq3r.jpg","first_air_date":"2023-10-19","name":"Theory of Big Money","vote_average":9.1,"vote_count":7},{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":"/pZhQBgAi42CVqwu1S2HN2Ty3Ewn.jpg","genre_ids":[10762],"id":124912,"origin_country":["NO"],"original_language":"no","original_name":"Kjempemaskiner","overview":"In Oiii''s new series for the little ones, Bamse Broom puts on his work clothes and joins good machine operators in their chopping, digging, drumming, noisy BIG MACHINES!","popularity":0.1301,"poster_path":"/fFIrOZtCtZZ8N38fVePxn3RuB2K.jpg","first_air_date":"2020-08-28","name":"Big Machines","vote_average":0,"vote_count":0}],"total_pages":12,"total_results":239}','2026-04-10 16:11:20');
